    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Dumb and demonic",
        "Description": "Hello Agents, Today your targets are 5 mercenarys that roam in and outside of the mansion. These targets were all apart of a wicked and demonic sacrifice on another worker at the mansion, but the funny thing is that the whole thing was caught on CCTV. Kill allthese dumb mercenarys each with a different accident so avenge the workers death. Goodluck\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as OM3RCENARY.",
